cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

The paper deals with generating videos from natural language descriptions, which involves tasks related to computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The model also involves learning and training components, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with video data, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
